    "question_id" : 6094575,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If class has only one empty constructor (like Activity or Fragment etc, android classes):</p>\n\n<pre><code>Class&lt;?&gt; myClass = Class.forName(\"com.example.MyClass\");    \nConstructor&lt;?&gt; constructor = myClass.getConstructors()[0];\n</code></pre>\n"
