  "title" : "Creating an instance using the class name and calling constructor",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a way to create an instance of a particular class given the class name (dynamic) and pass parameters to its constructor.</p>\n\n<p>Something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Object object = createInstance(\"mypackage.MyClass\",\"MyAttributeValue\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Where <code>\"MyAttributeValue\"</code> is an argument to the constructor of <code>MyClass</code>.</p>\n"
